{"sections":{"breadcrumbs":{"type":"breadcrumbs","settings":{"hide_mobile":false}},"section-slideshow":{"type":"section-slideshow","blocks":{"slide_1":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Klantenservice_Melanie.jpg","layout":"background","overlay_opacity":50,"color_palette":"scheme-94acd757-5569-4628-bd03-d75dff3f8f55","text_position":"align-center text-center","title":"<h1>We helpen je graag!<\/h1>","title_underline_style":"none","text":"<p><strong>Ons team staat voor je klaar op werkdagen tussen 09:00 & 20:00<\/strong><\/p>","show_first_link":false,"first_link_text":"Button","first_link_url":"\/","first_button_style":"primary plain","show_second_link":false,"second_link_text":"Button","second_link_url":"","second_button_style":"secondary plain"}}},"block_order":["slide_1"],"settings":{"height":"32\/9","width":"boxed","autoplay":false,"autoplay_seconds":3,"enable_controls":false,"height_mobile":"16\/9","spacing_desktop":50,"spacing_mobile":30}},"page-service-menu":{"type":"page-service-menu","settings":{"menu":"main-menu"}},"17653170088a29c23e":{"type":"apps","settings":{}},"section_custom_liquid_qEkFgh":{"type":"section-custom-liquid","disabled":true,"name":"Retour aanmelden","settings":{"custom_liquid":"<form id=\"quick-checkout-form\">\n  <button type=\"button\" class=\"button\" style=\"width: 100%; background-color: #FFd100; color: #fff; border: none; padding: 10px; font-size: 16px;\">\n    Retour Aanmelden\n  <\/button>\n<\/form>\n\n<script>\n  document.getElementById('quick-checkout-form').addEventListener('click', function() {\n    window.location.href = 'https:\/\/www.vctparts.nl\/pages\/retour-aanmelden';\n  });\n<\/script>","spacing_desktop":50,"spacing_mobile":30}},"17658296664de88cbe":{"type":"apps","blocks":{"asktimmy_ai_quick_ask_launcher_AWiEhk":{"type":"shopify:\/\/apps\/asktimmy-ai\/blocks\/quick_ask_launcher\/400790a8-f036-45a6-886a-4150d0e6f6aa","settings":{}}},"block_order":["asktimmy_ai_quick_ask_launcher_AWiEhk"],"settings":{}},"section_custom_html_WJWhgT":{"type":"section-custom-html","name":"t:sections.custom_html.presets.name","settings":{"custom_html":"","spacing_desktop":30,"spacing_mobile":30}},"section-faq":{"type":"section-faq","blocks":{"text_3yqHmh":{"type":"text","settings":{"faq_question":"Hoe retourneer ik mijn bestelling?","icon":"none","header_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Shipment-Upload--Streamline-Core.svg","header_image_svg":"","header_image_width":25,"faq_answer":"<p>Je vraagt <a href=\"\/pages\/retour-aanmelden\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Retour Aanmelden\">hier<\/a> <strong>eenvoudig een retourlabel<\/strong> aan via onze <strong>retourpagina<\/strong>. Deze vraag je aan met je email en ordernummer.<\/p>","page":"","image_width":465,"liquid":"","html":"","show_contact_form":false}},"faq_2":{"type":"text","settings":{"faq_question":"Kan ik mijn bestelling ook ophalen?","icon":"none","header_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Store-1--Streamline-Core.svg","header_image_svg":"","header_image_width":25,"faq_answer":"<p><strong>Ja<\/strong>, mits je eerst <strong>online besteld<\/strong> en dit aanvinkt bij de betaling. <strong>Zonder bestelling is dit niet mogelijk.<\/strong><br\/><br\/>Afhalen kan op <strong>werkdagen<\/strong> tussen <strong>12:00 en 15:00,<\/strong> na <strong>bevestiging <\/strong>dat je bestelling klaarligt.<br\/><br\/><strong>Buiten deze tijden zijn wij niet aanwezig<\/strong> en kunnen we je bestelling niet meegeven.<\/p>","page":"","image_width":465,"liquid":"","html":"","show_contact_form":false}},"text_FdJzan":{"type":"text","settings":{"faq_question":"Wanneer ontvang ik mijn bestelling?","icon":"none","header_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Startup--Streamline-Core.svg","header_image_svg":"","header_image_width":25,"faq_answer":"<p><strong>Nederland<\/strong><br\/>Voor onze klanten in Nederland geldt dat wij in <strong>97.5% van de gevallen<\/strong> de volgende dag leveren wanneer je op werkdagen voor 20:00 uur bestelt. Dit betekent dat je er bijna altijd op kunt rekenen dat je bestelling de volgende dag bezorgd wordt.<\/p><p><strong>België<\/strong><br\/>Voor onze Belgische klanten kunnen we in <strong>92.3% van de gevallen<\/strong> garanderen dat je bestelling de volgende dag bezorgd wordt wanneer je op werkdagen voor 20:00 uur bestelt. Ondanks onze inspanningen zijn er helaas situaties waarbij bezorging de volgende dag niet mogelijk is.<\/p>","page":"","image_width":465,"liquid":"","html":"","show_contact_form":false}},"faq_1":{"type":"text","settings":{"faq_question":"Hoeveel dagen bedenktijd heb ik?","icon":"none","header_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Circle-Clock--Streamline-Core.svg","header_image_svg":"","header_image_width":25,"faq_answer":"<p>Bij VCTparts heb je <strong>altijd 30 dagen<\/strong> bedenktijd. Dit betekend dat je een volle maand hebt om je te bedenken en de order te retourneren.<\/p>","page":"","image_width":465,"liquid":"","html":"","show_contact_form":false}},"text_qwJbj7":{"type":"text","settings":{"faq_question":"Hebben jullie een fysieke locatie?","icon":"none","header_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Warehouse-1--Streamline-Core.svg","header_image_svg":"","header_image_width":25,"faq_answer":"<p>We hebben <strong>geen fysieke winkel<\/strong>. Wij hebben alleen een <strong>verzendmagazijn <\/strong>in Hardenberg.<\/p><p><strong>Afhalen van je bestelling<\/strong><\/p><ol><li>Plaats eerst je <strong>bestelling online<\/strong>.<br\/><\/li><li>Kies bij het afrekenen voor <strong>afhalen<\/strong>.<br\/><\/li><li>Wacht op de <strong>bevestiging in je mail<\/strong> dat je bestelling klaarstaat.<br\/><\/li><li>Haal je bestelling op werkdagen op tussen <strong>12:00 en 15:00 uur<\/strong>.<\/li><\/ol><p>Zonder bestelling kun je <strong>geen aankopen<\/strong> bij ons doen en\/of afhalen.<\/p>","page":"","image_width":465,"liquid":"","html":"","show_contact_form":false}},"text_X9M9WF":{"type":"text","settings":{"faq_question":"Hoe dien ik een klacht in?","icon":"none","header_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Synchronize-Warning--Streamline-Core.svg","header_image_svg":"","header_image_width":25,"faq_answer":"<p>Heeft u een klacht over onze producten of dienstverlening? Neem dan contact met ons op via het contactformulier. Wij reageren binnen 14 dagen inhoudelijk op uw klacht.<\/p><p>Bent u niet tevreden met onze afhandeling? Dan kunt u uw klacht voorleggen aan de Geschillencommissie Thuiswinkel via <a href=\"https:\/\/www.sgc.nl\">www.sgc.nl<\/a>.<\/p>","page":"","image_width":465,"liquid":"","html":"","show_contact_form":false}},"text_LyYe3g":{"type":"text","settings":{"faq_question":"Wanneer wordt mijn retour verwerkt?","icon":"none","header_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Coin-Share--Streamline-Core.svg","header_image_svg":"","header_image_width":25,"faq_answer":"<p>Wij verwerken retouren vrijwel altijd <strong>binnen 5 werkdagen<\/strong> na binnenkomst.<br\/><br\/>De terugbetaling gaat altijd via de <strong>gebruikte betaalmethode<\/strong>. Dit kan nog 3 dagen duren. Vaak is dit echter sneller.<\/p><p>We willen je graag vragen <strong>minimaal 7 dagen te wachten<\/strong> na aankomst bij ons pand alvorens contact op te nemen. Bedankt voor je begrip!<\/p>","page":"","image_width":465,"liquid":"","html":"","show_contact_form":false}},"text_NKbknr":{"type":"text","settings":{"faq_question":"Kan ik mijn bestelling nog wijzigen?","icon":"none","header_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Shopping-Basket-2--Streamline-Core.svg","header_image_svg":"","header_image_width":25,"faq_answer":"<p>Het is helaas <strong>niet mogelijk<\/strong> om je order nog aan te passen. Wel kunnen we je order annuleren zodat je een nieuwe order kunt plaatsen.<\/p>","page":"","image_width":465,"liquid":"","html":"","show_contact_form":false}},"text_w4KEPH":{"type":"text","settings":{"faq_question":"Zijn de prijzen inclusief btw?","icon":"none","header_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Dollar-Coin-1--Streamline-Core.svg","header_image_svg":"","header_image_width":25,"faq_answer":"<p><strong>Ja<\/strong>, alle prijzen op onze website zijn inclusief 21% btw. Dit geld voor zakelijke en particuliere klanten.<\/p>","page":"","image_width":465,"liquid":"","html":"","show_contact_form":false}}},"block_order":["text_3yqHmh","faq_2","text_FdJzan","faq_1","text_qwJbj7","text_X9M9WF","text_LyYe3g","text_NKbknr","text_w4KEPH"],"settings":{"alignment":"left","compact":false,"title":"<h2>Veelgestelde vragen<\/h2>","title_underline_style":"none","spacing_desktop":50,"spacing_mobile":30}},"section-contact-form":{"type":"section-contact-form","blocks":{"0fd44d31-da56-43fe-972d-74b438cbb328":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Naam","placeholder":"Jan Janssen","required":true}},"b8774408-fd65-4d42-865e-40eb5da3e9ee":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Ordernummer","placeholder":"#2320000","required":false}},"30c68dd5-0daf-4c67-9e87-30fae9f6db2e":{"type":"email","settings":{"title":"Email","placeholder":"Email@emailadres.nl"}},"e70b7df4-5299-4c87-b7a3-7f0ab2f6cd55":{"type":"tel","settings":{"title":"Tel. Nummer","placeholder":"+31 6 00000000","required":false}},"7f5b90a3-0ea1-466d-a8bb-fb174e340aed":{"type":"textarea","settings":{"title":"Bericht","placeholder":"Vraag over een bestelling? Vermeld dan altijd je ordernummer, hierdoor kunnen we sneller helpen.","required":true}}},"block_order":["0fd44d31-da56-43fe-972d-74b438cbb328","b8774408-fd65-4d42-865e-40eb5da3e9ee","30c68dd5-0daf-4c67-9e87-30fae9f6db2e","e70b7df4-5299-4c87-b7a3-7f0ab2f6cd55","7f5b90a3-0ea1-466d-a8bb-fb174e340aed"],"settings":{"alignment":"start","title":"<h2>Contactformulier<\/h2>","title_underline_style":"none","button_style":"primary plain","show_placeholder":true,"compact":false,"spacing_desktop":30,"spacing_mobile":30}},"page-service-info-blocks":{"type":"page-service-info-blocks","blocks":{"18ebb386-ad40-4c3f-8386-2c45cb1a6cb2":{"type":"information","settings":{"color_palette":"scheme-3","title":"Account info","text":"<p><a href=\"\/account\" title=\"\/accou